its the sort of thing where you make up your mind and you cant 
even feel anything until later your first responsibility is to 
your children 
at first kristine knutson wasnt sure what was best for her 
children 
from her kitchen window in kuwait the minnesota native with 
four children under the age of 8 could hear bombs and see 
